{"html":"<h2>Multiset Rewriting Rules</h2><br/>\n<p class=\"monospace rules\"><span class=\"hl_keyword\">rule</span> (<span class=\"hl_keyword\">modulo</span> E) Send:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> Fr( ~k ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">--&gt;</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> Out( diff(~k, ~k) ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_keyword\">left</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_keyword\">rule</span> (<span class=\"hl_keyword\">modulo</span> E) Send:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> Fr( ~k ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">--&gt;</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> Out( ~k ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_keyword\">right</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_keyword\">rule</span> (<span class=\"hl_keyword\">modulo</span> E) Send:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> Fr( ~k ), In( extra ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">--&gt;</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> Out( ~k ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span></p><br/>\n","title":"Multiset rewriting rules and restrictions - unprocessed"}